{"id":"cbc16ccb-8266-4c0a-b831-4450e3951890","name":"Modern Fantasy Academy","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>[Updated]</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 198, 0);\"><strong>Hey You!</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 198, 0);\"><strong>Yes, you!</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 198, 0);\"><strong>.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 198, 0);\"><strong>.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 198, 0);\"><strong>Would you like to explore what it feels like to have fantasy things in modern world?</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 242, 153);\"><strong>Altherion Academy</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2c91bb54-69d9-40f8-b8ae-01eda7a2559e_2c8762af-797c-4e57-b2db-a7fd706ab717.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>A prestigious magic school, known for it's extravagant things and for graduating many talented and successful people such as legendary witches and wizards.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 242, 153);\"><strong>Ignisia Tower</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2c91bb54-69d9-40f8-b8ae-01eda7a2559e_3f2dcbec-f6ea-4faa-8053-1da931f57aff.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 242, 153);\"><strong>Arcane Nexus</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2c91bb54-69d9-40f8-b8ae-01eda7a2559e_ef034775-e7a5-4c4b-9f77-36873018967c.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 242, 153);\"><strong>Solstice Haven</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2c91bb54-69d9-40f8-b8ae-01eda7a2559e_487e7450-1e75-4c00-be4c-cf4afb5cd6a8.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Wondering why these buildings exist?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>I'll explain in some kind short sentence!</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 143, 50);\"><strong>Ignisia Tower - </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">A place that usually used for school events, the welcoming new students event also held here.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 80, 201);\"><strong>Arcane Nexus - </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">A place that used for students to train their magic, attending clubs they joined (all the clubs rooms is in here) or simply train their abilities</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(21, 226, 159);\"><strong>Solstice Haven - </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Students dorms that has cafetaria, lounge with small library, and field in first floor. Oh, there's swimming pool too on the back of the building.</span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(11, 193, 241);\"><strong>The Guardians of Altherion Academy</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/2c91bb54-69d9-40f8-b8ae-01eda7a2559e_8a92513d-b458-42d4-ba8d-d1c10079008c.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Frostail &amp; Xyvaroth</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Enjoy the bot!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>I'm not a native English speakers, I apologize if there's a wrong grammars or something like that. If the bot speaks for you,","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"2c91bb54-69d9-40f8-b8ae-01eda7a2559e_6f6087cd-16fc-400a-8b7d-eebac9aa88a0.webp","creator":"Nyxia_Morana","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🔮 Magical","👭 Multiple","🪢 Scenario","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":4034,"messages":137419,"created_at":"2024-12-14T07:30:10.012560+00:00"}